CRA Ltd. say e don gree sell di 40% stake for im Howick mine for state of New South Wales to Mitsubishi Development Pty, Japan.

Di money, no be im dem reveal.

Di agreement dey subject to government approval.

: RAP get di Howick coal wey dey Oct. 20 when e buy British Petroleum Co, for $275 million.

CRA con talk sey e dey find partner for di mine, wey dey produce more dan three million pound of coal every year.

CRA na 49% of di RTK corp wey dey Britain.

